  "description": {
    "zh": "训练是永远不嫌多的，尤其是在塔科夫里。学会与步枪融为一体，应该是你在主动控制步枪，而不是步枪控制你。在进行行动任务时，总会耗尽弹药的时候，所以有必要训练你的装弹技巧。总有一天及时装满弹匣可能会救你一命，你以后会感谢我的。",
    "en": "Theres never enough training, especially here in Tarkov. Learn to become one with your rifle, it should be you who controls the rifle and not the rifle that controls you. You will run out of ammo in fights for sure, so train your mag drills. Filling up your magazines in time might save your life one day, you can thank me later."
  },
